text: Gert Bjerendal (born 12 June 1955) is a Swedish archer. Bjerendal competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics.Gert BjerendalGert BJERENDAL ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden
